y groups heal regenerating songs most have good faction classes. There is a lot of good things about a bard.I could say many good things about mages also. They have the best pets,good at nuking, can root. Good at soloing good at pvp i mean there is so many different aspects especially bard and mage. So if your a mage sometimes they wonder what is so good about a bard and vice versa. The reason that I picked a paladin is because they get good weapons,look cool,good faction,heal,good tankers,good armor,good starting area,root,stun and basically are very fun. If your a cleric all you do is heal canget boring to some people. As a warrior you dont get an fun spells can also get boring. But i can entertain myself with both. My main summary I guess is pick what class is the best for you doesent matter what other people think. Be nice and respectful to each other its a game relax!<BR>
